# grid of images
feh -t .
feh -m .

# give transparent bg for grid of images
feh -t -b trans .
feh -m -b trans .

# open all images in each individual window
feh -w .

Keyboard Shortcut Configuration
===============================

cat > ~/.config/feh/keys << EOF
scroll_down  Down
scroll_up    Up
scroll_left  Left
scroll_right Right
scroll_up_page Prior
scroll_down_page Next
zoom_in plus equal
zoom_out minus
EOF
